{"title":"Bikepacking Roots Allegheny Crossroads Bikepacking Loop","link":"https://theradavist.com/bikepacking-roots-allegheny-crossroads/","date":1740485605000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-10-Photo-by.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-10-Photo-by.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-10-Photo-by.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-10-Photo-by.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>The Allegheny Mountains of West Virginia, Maryland, and Pennsylvania. The Allegheny Crossroads Bikepacking loop was created by <a href=\"https://canalbyways.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Geoff Patterson</a>, creator of the C&amp;O Canal Byways route collection.</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-09-Photo-by.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-09-Photo-by.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-09-Photo-by.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-09-Photo-by.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>⁠The Allegheny Crossroads Bikepacking Loop crosses the Allegheny Mountains and explores the rugged foothills on each side of the Eastern Continental Divide. Meandering between Morgantown, WV to the west and Hancock, MD to the east, the route connects public lands in three states, is easily accessible by train, and offers many camping options plus the occasional opportunity for more luxurious lodging. </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-19-Photo-by.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-19-Photo-by.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-19-Photo-by.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-19-Photo-by.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-02-Photo-by.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-02-Photo-by.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-02-Photo-by.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-02-Photo-by.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-05-Photo-by-Geoff-Patterson.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-05-Photo-by-Geoff-Patterson.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-05-Photo-by-Geoff-Patterson.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Allegheny-Crossroads-05-Photo-by-Geoff-Patterson.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>As you conquer the many ridges of the Alleghenies, you’ll frequently experience long periods of solitude before you exit the forest to a small town or rail trail for a brief respite from the mountainous terrain. </p>\n<p><em>Thank you to AJ DeLauder (<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/snallygaster.bikepacking/?locale=French&amp;hl=am-et\" target=\"_blank\">@snallygaster.bikepacking</a> route creator) and Jacob Rex (<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/snallygaster.bikepacking/?locale=French&amp;hl=am-et\" target=\"_blank\">@hellbenderbikepackingwv</a> route creator). About 25% of this route overlaps their routes (with permission). Find more info on the route at <a href=\"https://bikepackingroots.org/project/allegheny-crossroads-bikepacking-loop/\" target=\"_blank\">Bikepacking Roots</a>.</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/bikepacking-roots-allegheny-crossroads/\">Bikepacking Roots Allegheny Crossroads Bikepacking Loop</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"1dd4f210fffa96af9e2c406b909d0ff3bec7f3782da81ad9b7d2c472ab88bcbd","category":"Cycling"}